oc:kn_5d895b93 a oc:Heuristic,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When composing automated messages to channels with many members" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Use @mentions sparingly to avoid notification fatigue among team members." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Excessive mentions degrade the signal-to-noise ratio and cause users to mute or ignore the channel." .

oc:kn_7b886fb5 a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:KnownIssue ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When setting up notification-only workflows that don't require interactive responses" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Use incoming webhooks for one-way notification scenarios (CI/CD alerts, deployment status) rather than bot-based messaging." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Webhooks are simpler to configure, require fewer permissions, and are more reliable for unidirectional notifications." .

oc:kn_8588c9b6 a oc:Constraint,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When configuring Teams automation app registration and permissions" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Request minimal permission scopes — only request the Graph API permissions actually needed for the workflow." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Over-privileged apps create security risks and may fail admin approval in enterprise environments." ;
    oc:severityLevel "HIGH" .

oc:kn_9bda0ed0 a oc:DesignPrinciple,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When sending messages requiring user interaction (approvals, forms, status checks)" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Use Adaptive Cards for rich interactive content instead of plain text messages when users need to take action." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Adaptive Cards provide structured, interactive UI within Teams that plain messages cannot achieve." .

oc:kn_d24f8f11 a oc:Constraint,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When automating high-volume Teams messaging or notifications" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Respect Microsoft Graph API rate limits when sending messages or making API calls." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Exceeding rate limits causes throttling, delayed delivery, and potential temporary blocks on the application." ;
    oc:severityLevel "HIGH" .

oc:kn_dc76cef0 a oc:Heuristic,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When bot or automation responds to user messages in channels" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Reply in threads to maintain conversation context rather than posting top-level channel messages for responses." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Threading keeps channels organized and makes conversation context easy to follow." .

